<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
<title>LIKIMO EGZAMINAS</title>
<style>
:root{
--bg1:#fff5f8;
--bg2:#eef5ff;
--accent:#ff5c8d;
--gold:#d4af37;
}
body{
margin:0;
font-family:Inter,Arial,sans-serif;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--bg1),var(--bg2));
color:#222;
}
.container{max-width:1000px;margin:auto;padding:24px}
.card{
background:rgba(255,255,255,.95);
backdrop-filter:blur(8px);
border-radius:24px;
padding:28px;
margin:20px 0;
box-shadow:0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
}
.hero{
text-align:center;
padding:60px 20px;
}
.hero h1{
font-size:4rem;
margin:0;
letter-spacing:3px;
}
.hero h3{opacity:.8}
.flags{font-size:2rem}
button{
background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent),#ff86aa);
color:white;
border:none;
padding:14px 28px;
border-radius:14px;
font-weight:700;
cursor:pointer;
}
.progress{height:14px;background:#ddd;border-radius:20px;overflow:hidden}
.bar{height:100%;width:0;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--accent),#ff8eb2)}
.hidden{display:none}
.contract{
background:linear-gradient(180deg,#fffef8,#fff8e6);
border:8px solid var(--gold);
border-radius:28px;
padding:40px;
position:relative;
box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.15);
}
.contract:before{
content:"";
position:absolute;
inset:12px;
border:2px solid var(--gold);
border-radius:18px;
pointer-events:none;
}
.title{
text-align:center;
font-size:2.5rem;
font-weight:900;
letter-spacing:2px;
}
.subtitle{
text-align:center;
font-style:italic;
opacity:.8;
}
.article{
padding:12px 0;
border-bottom:1px dashed #d9c27a;
}
.stamp{
margin-top:25px;
text-align:center;
font-size:80px;
font-weight:900;
color:#d40000;
transform:rotate(-10deg);
opacity:.85;
}
.signature{
text-align:center;
margin-top:30px;
padding-top:20px;
border-top:2px solid #d9c27a;
}
img{max-width:100%;border-radius:18px}

label{display:block;margin:8px 0} textarea{width:100%;height:120px}
#countdownBox{position:fixed;top:10px;right:10px;background:white;padding:10px 14px;border-radius:12px;box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.12);z-index:9999}
.heart{position:fixed;font-size:24px;pointer-events:none;animation:fall 4s linear forwards}
@keyframes fall{from{transform:translateY(-50px)}to{transform:translateY(110vh)}}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="countdownBox">
<b>Days until Paulina invades France:</b><br>
<span id="countdownDays">...</span>
</div>

<div class="container">
<div id="home" class="card center">
<h1>LIKIMO EGZAMINAS</h1>
<h3>The Fate Examination</h3>
<p>🇫🇷 ❤️ 🇱🇹 ✈️</p>
<button onclick="startQuiz()">Start The Adventure</button>
</div>

<div id="quiz" class="hidden">
<div class="progress"><div id="bar" class="bar"></div></div>
<h2 id="title"></h2>
<div id="content"></div>
<div class="center"><button onclick="nextStep()">Continue</button></div>
</div>

<div id="transition" class="hidden"></div>

<div id="final" class="hidden">
<div class="contract">
<div class="title">OFFICIAL MARRIAGE CONTRACT</div>
<p class="subtitle">
Certified by the International Department of Fate,
Bad Decisions & Unexpected Feelings
</p>

<div class="article">
<b>Party A:</b> Paulina The Traveller<br>
<small>Professional Globe Explorer, Phone Call Avoider, Fate Enthusiast</small>
</div>

<div class="article">
<b>Party B:</b> Jean‑Christophe<br>
<small>The Tall, Handsome, Hilarious, Brilliant and Totally Humble French Gentleman</small>
</div>

<div class="article">
<b>ARTICLE I</b><br>
His jokes are legally classified as funny.
</div>

<div class="article">
<b>ARTICLE II</b><br>
Minimum one adventure per month.
</div>

<div class="article">
<b>ARTICLE III</b><br>
Phone calls may not be avoided using fate, dead batteries,
airport Wi‑Fi, poor signal, mysterious disappearances,
or suspiciously convenient naps.
</div>

<div class="article">
<b>ARTICLE IV</b><br>
Unlimited teasing is fully authorized.
</div>

<div class="article">
<b>ARTICLE V</b><br>
Emergency vegetables and kisses protocol activated. 🥕💋
</div>

<div class="article">
<b>ARTICLE VI</b><br>
In the event of excessive cuteness,
both parties must immediately book another trip.
</div>

<div class="article">
<b>ARTICLE VII</b><br>
If either party accidentally falls more in love,
they are required to pretend it was fate.
</div>

<div class="stamp">APPROVED</div>

<div class="signature">
🇫🇷 France &nbsp; • &nbsp; 🇱🇹 Lithuania &nbsp; • &nbsp; ❤️ Fate &nbsp; • &nbsp; ✈️ Aviation
<br><br>
Validity: <b>Forever*</b>
<br>
<small>*Terms and conditions may be modified after excessive flirting.</small>
</div>
</div>
<div class="card" style="text-align:center">
<img src="contract.png" style="max-width:100%">
<h2>Congratulations.</h2>
<p>You have completed LIKIMO EGZAMINAS.</p>
<p>Reward unlocked: Voucher for one amazing weekend in France.</p>
<p><b>The Frenchman is waiting.</b></p>
</div>
</div>

</div>

<script>
const levels=[
{title:"Level 1: Simple (The Remnants of Malta)",html:`
<div class='card'>
<p><b>1. Where did we meet and how?</b></p>
<label>A) At Havana, and with just one wave of my hand you came over (like a good little puppy).</label>
<label>B) On a rooftop, I arrived by helicopter.</label>
<label>C) We’ve never actually met.</label>

<p><b>2. Who is the final boss I had to fight outside for 15 minutes?</b></p>
<label>A) The Havana bouncer.</label>
<label>B) Paula acting as a full-on anti-flirt shield.</label>
<label>C) A late Uber driver.</label>

<p><b>3. The fight outside happened because:</b></p>
<label>A) I was too handsome, so she was scared you’d never come back.</label>
<label>B) She knew you were going to cave in (or maybe you cave in for every guy).</label>
<label>C) She was sick of you ending your nights with random guys.</label>

<p><b>4. If Paulina had listened to Paula that night, today we would be:</b></p>
<label>A) Hooking up.</label>
<label>B) Thinking about each other because we could never forget one another.</label>
<label>C) Completely ignoring each other.</label>

<p><b>5. What memory do you have left from our night at my apartment?</b></p>
<textarea></textarea></div>`,
transition:"Congratulations. You survived the Malta Investigation. Perform a 15-second victory dance immediately."},

{title:"Level 2: Medium",html:`<div class='card'>
<p><b>1.</b> Why do you spend your days laughing alone at your phone?</p>
<label>A) Because of cat videos.</label><label>B) Because I am a comedy genius.</label><label>C) It’s a nervous laugh caused by stress.</label>

<p><b>2.</b> True or False: At this point, my texts deserve a Nobel Prize in comedy.</p>
<label>A) True, I validate this 100%.</label><label>B) False, you're trying a bit too hard.</label><label>C) I shall only answer in the presence of my lawyer.</label>

<p><b>3.</b> When I suggest a phone call, your reaction looks like:</p>
<label>A) "Yeaaaah, can't wait!" (Lie).</label><label>B) A ninja dodge via text 2 hours later.</label><label>C) "Sorry, my phone is dead for the next 3 days."</label>

<p><b>4.</b> Who is the most positive, chill, and "I don't give a damn" person in the world?</p>
<label>A) A Buddhist monk in the middle of Tibet.</label><label>B) You, living day by day with zero stress.</label><label>C) Bob Marley.</label>

<p><b>5.</b> What is your official life philosophy?</p>
<label>A) "Wake up, work, sleep, repeat."</label><label>B) "Fate makes things happen, and I never stay at home."</label><label>C) "Saving up for retirement."</label>
</div>`,transition:"Not bad. For a Russian, you're doing surprisingly well. Compatibility level: 64%."},

{title:"Level 3: Difficult (The Moment of Truth)",html:`<div class='card'>
<p><b>1.</b> Let's analyze the romance levels in our texts. Who is the official whipped one?</p>
<label>A) Me, I throw all my love out there 24/7.</label><label>B) You, but it’s so deeply hidden you need a decoder.</label><label>C) It’s perfectly balanced (False).</label>

<p><b>2.</b> Complete the sentence: "If I show that I am in love..."</p>
<label>A) "...You just reply with a thumbs-up emoji."</label><label>B) "...You show it back to me."</label><label>C) "...You do nothing because you don't love me."</label>

<p><b>3.</b> On a scale from 1 to "Glacier in Iceland", how much do you show your feelings over text?</p>
<label>A) 10/10 (In a parallel universe).</label><label>B) 2/10 (But the mystery makes your charm—False).</label><label>C) Fate knows, no need to write it down.</label>

<p><b>4.</b> What is your personal record for the longest time spent locked inside your house?</p>
<label>A) 24 hours (and you almost had a panic attack).</label><label>B) 1 month.</label><label>C) You don't have a house, you live out of suitcases.</label>

<p><b>5.</b> If I give you a dictionary of synonyms for the word "Love", you use it to:</p>
<label>A) Write me a poem.</label><label>B) Balance a wobbly table.</label><label>C) Read it on the plane to your next trip.</label>
</div>`,transition:"You're getting closer. I am considering getting down on one knee. 🧎"},

{title:"Level 4: Expert (The 1-Month Countdown)",html:`<div class='card'>
<p><b>1.</b> I have organized EVERYTHING for your visit in a month. Your only mission is to:</p>
<label>A) Not cancel.</label><label>B) Show up with your most beautiful smile and your travel bag.</label><label>C) Answer my phone calls while on the plane.</label>

<p><b>2.</b> Test question: Are you down to skydive out of a plane with me when you arrive?</p>
<label>A) Hell yeah, not even scared!</label><label>B) I’d rather die (or go back to Havana).</label><label>C) If fate decides the parachute opens, then okay.</label>

<p><b>3.</b> If you don't like the itinerary for your trip, you have the right to:</p>
<label>A) Complain via text (since you hate phone calls).</label><label>B) Absolutely nothing, the schedule is locked by tech.</label><label>C) Leave immediately for another country.</label>

<p><b>4.</b> What is my biggest fear regarding your visit in a month?</p>
<label>A) I am never scared.</label><label>B) That your friend from Malta shows up out of nowhere.</label><label>C) That you refuse to go skydiving.</label>

<p><b>5.</b> What is the mandatory dress code for your arrival?</p>
<label>A) The Havana outfit (nostalgia).</label><label>B) A ring.</label><label>C) Naked.</label>
</div>`,transition:"Almost there. One more effort and I might accidentally put a ring on your finger. 💍"},

{title:"Level 5: Fiancé / Marry Me (Impossible)",html:`<div class='card'>
<p><b>1.</b> If the skydiving goes well and we survive, the next logical step is:</p>
<label>A) A McDonald's to celebrate.</label><label>B) A round-trip ticket to Las Vegas.</label><label>C) You finally confess your feelings out loud.</label>

<p><b>2.</b> Since you believe in fate, what does it say about us meeting at 4 AM at Havana?</p>
<label>A) That the DJ was trash but the alignment of the planets was perfect.</label><label>B) It was pure luck, don't get ahead of yourself.</label><label>C) That you're going to have to deal with my humor for the rest of your life.</label>

<p><b>3.</b> If you had to commit (to me), would you do it?</p>
<label>A) Of course, you’re the best guy I’ve ever met.</label><label>B) Yes, but you’re not the best.</label><label>C) No, you’re not good enough.</label>

<p><b>4.</b> The secret marriage contract states that:</b></p>
<label>A) We must see each other at least one weekend a month.</label><label>B) You have to be emotional with me.</label><label>C) I handle the humor, you handle the chill.</label>

<p><b>5.</b> Bodycount (how many people did you kill): +5 +10 +15</p>

<p><b>6.</b> To validate this quiz and win your voucher for an amazing weekend upon arrival, you must:</p>
<label><input type='checkbox' id='a'> A) Click "Validate" and send me a cute text.</label>
<label><input type='checkbox' id='b'> B) Promise not to run away after 2 hours.</label>
<label><input type='checkbox' id='c'> C) Send me an outfit picture every single day.</label>
<div id='err' style='color:red'></div>
</div>`}
];
let i=0;
function startQuiz(){home.style.display='none';quiz.classList.remove('hidden');render();}
function render(){title.innerText=levels[i].title;content.innerHTML=levels[i].html;bar.style.width=(i/5*100)+'%';}
function nextStep(){
 if(i===4){
   if(!(a.checked&&b.checked&&c.checked)){err.innerText='You must select ALL options to unlock the marriage contract.';return;}
   quiz.classList.add('hidden');final.classList.remove('hidden');return;
 }
 transition.innerHTML='<div class="card">'+levels[i].transition+'<br><br><button onclick="cont()">Continue</button></div>';
 quiz.classList.add('hidden');transition.classList.remove('hidden');
}
function cont(){transition.classList.add('hidden');quiz.classList.remove('hidden');i++;render();}

function updateCountdown(){
 const target=new Date('2026-06-26T00:00:00');
 const days=Math.max(0,Math.ceil((target-new Date())/86400000));
 const el=document.getElementById('countdownDays');
 if(el) el.textContent=days+' days';
}
updateCountdown();

function heartRain(){
 for(let i=0;i<60;i++){
   const h=document.createElement('div');
   h.className='heart';
   h.innerHTML='❤️';
   h.style.left=(Math.random()*100)+'vw';
   h.style.animationDelay=(Math.random()*2)+'s';
   document.body.appendChild(h);
   setTimeout(()=>h.remove(),5000);
 }
}

const oldNextStep = window.nextStep;
if(oldNextStep){
 window.nextStep=function(){
   try{
     if(window.i===4 && document.getElementById('a')?.checked && document.getElementById('b')?.checked && document.getElementById('c')?.checked){
       heartRain();
     }
   }catch(e){}
   return oldNextStep.apply(this,arguments);
 }
}
</script>
</body></html>
